    "improvements_made": "Merged PROCESSOR_CONFIGURATION into TASK_DEFINITION as a JSON column to simplify the model while preserving configurability. Added comprehensive audit fields (created_by, created_at, updated_at) to all primary entities. Defined a many‑to‑many relationship between EXECUTION_INSTANCE and SCHEDULED_TASK via the EXECUTION_SCHEDULE junction table to support scenarios where an execution instance handles multiple scheduled tasks or retries. Introduced tenant_id foreign keys on TASK_DEFINITION and other tenant‑scoped entities for strict isolation. Updated cardinalities and optionalities for repeat configuration, exception logs, and lock info. Added missing relationships (e.g., TASK_EXECUTION → TASK_DEFINITION) for clarity. Ensured naming consistency across timestamps and identifiers."
